Amazing customer service! I ordered 2 of the same drinks and they ran out of tea before the second drink was made. After patiently waiting on the side, no one let me know why I was still waiting or for so long. I stepped up and politely asked if they’d forgotten about my other drink. The gentlemen let me know they were brewing more green tea and it would just be a few more minutes. Then the manager asked if I wanted to try it with white tea instead which she said was similar in taste. I said sure why not and stepped back to wait. The manager then called me back up to the counter and gave me courtesy gift cards for the inconvenience. That was unexpected and greatly appreciated.  By the way, she was right...the white tea lemonade was just as good! Thank you Starbucks!
